PersonalMission.Name: LT-12: The Ghost
PersonalMission.Description: Good concealment increases your chances of survival in battle. Light tanks have great concealment abilities, thanks to their relatively low silhouettes.
PersonalMission.Hint: Once the enemy spots you, you will have to stay constantly on the move. But if you have not yet been spotted, find a position in a bush where you can stay concealed while lighting up the enemy. Equip your tank for stealth beforehand.

Primary.Conditions: Enable your allies to cause 3,000 HP of damage to enemy vehicles by spotting them. Remain unspotted at the moment when the damage is caused
